annel for a 320 MHz EHT SU transmission or EHT sound-\r\ning NDP\r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent) \r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent)\r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent)\r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent)\r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent) \r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent) \r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent) \r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent) \r\nEHT-SIG \r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG\r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG\r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG\r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG\r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG \r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG \r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG \r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent) \r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent) \r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent) \r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent)\r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent) \r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent) \r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent)\r\nU-SIG Overflow and Number of Non-OFDMA Users (if \r\npresent) \r\nEHT-SIG \r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG\r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nUser Specific field\r\nEHT-SIG\r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG\r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG\r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG \r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG \r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\nEHT-SIG \r\ncontent \r\nchannel 1\r\n80MHz frequency subblock 480MHz frequency subblock 380MHz frequency subblock 280MHz frequency subblock 1\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nDUP\r\nxOne User field for an EHT SU transmission\r\nxZero User fiel